 <fr:p>Suppose that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00MH.xml"
addr="jms-00MH"
title="Countable set">countable</fr:link>. We must find a <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00M8.xml"
addr="jms-00M8"
title="Surjection">surjection</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {N}\twoheadrightarrow  A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>; if <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is empty, this is the same as to find a <fr:link
type="local"
