href="jms-00ME.xml"
addr="jms-00ME"
title="Enumerable set">enumerations</fr:link> of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> respectively. Then the function <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[e_A\times  e_B\colon  \mathbb {N}\times \mathbb {N}\to  A\times  B]]></fr:tex> can be seen to be <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00M8.xml"
